history.proof: intros. induction l as [|x xs IH]. - reflexivity. - simpl. rewrite IH. rewrite (H x). hauto lq: on depth: 3.

exceptions.tactic: intros A f g l H.
intros A' f g l H.
intros A' f' g l H.
intros A' f' g' l H.
intros A' f' g' l' H.
intros A' f' g' l' H'.

original: intros. intros A f g l H. induction l as [|x xs IH]. - reflexivity. - simpl. rewrite IH. rewrite (H x). reflexivity.
